dataset_id: MEaSUREs Multi-year Greenland Ice Sheet Velocity Mosaic V001
title: MEaSUREs Multi-year Greenland Ice Sheet Velocity Mosaic V001
summary: This data set, part of the NASA Making Earth System Data Records for Use in Research Environments (MEaSUREs) program, contains a multi-year ice-sheet-wide velocity mosaic for Greenland, derived from Interferometric Synthetic Aperture Radar (InSAR), Synthetic Aperture Radar (SAR), and Landsat 8 optical imagery data. See Greenland Ice Mapping Project (GIMP) for related data.
